"2 (3 1/2-lb.) racks beef back ribs","1/3 cup kosher salt","1/4 cup finely ground medium-roast coffee beans","3 tablespoons black pepper","2 tablespoons paprika","2 tablespoons chili powder","2 handfulls wood chunks for smoking (oak, hickory, or mesquite)","1 cup cola soft drink or other dark cola soft drink","1 cup ketchup","1/2 cup brewed coffee","1/4 cup dark molasses","2 tablespoons sherry vinegar","2 tablespoons Worcestershire sauce","1/2 teaspoon chili powder","1/2 teaspoon kosher salt","1/8 teaspoon garlic powder","1/8 teaspoon onion powder"